## Source Material Attribution

The methodologies distilled in this skill set are derived from:

**《原则:应对变化中的世界秩序》** (Principles for Dealing with the Changing World Order)
**作者**: 瑞·达利欧 (Ray Dalio)
**出版社**: 中信出版社 (Chinese edition)

The skills represent original AI-applicable interpretations of the book's
methodology. They are not direct excerpts. Users are encouraged to read the
original book for full context.